{"id":37981,"date":"2022-07-19T14:43:55","date_gmt":"2022-07-19T10:43:55","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/?p=37981"},"modified":"2022-07-19T14:43:55","modified_gmt":"2022-07-19T10:43:55","slug":"amazing-iman","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2022\/07\/19\/amazing-iman\/","title":{"rendered":"Hadith on Believers: Amazing faith of those who never saw Prophets"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>Anas reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201c<strong>Who in creation has the most astonishing faith?<\/strong>\u201d They said, \u201cThe angels.\u201d The Prophet said, \u201c<strong>But how could the angels not believe?<\/strong>\u201d They said, \u201cThe prophets.\u201d The Prophet said, \u201c<strong>But the prophets were given divine revelation, so how could they not believe?<\/strong>\u201d They said, \u201cTheir companions.\u201d The Prophet said, \u201c<strong>The companions were with their prophets, so how could they not believe? Rather, the people with the most astonishing faith are those who come after you and they find a book of divine revelation, thus they believe in it and follow it. They are the people with the most astonishing faith.<\/strong>\u201d<\/p>\n<p>Source: Musnad al-Bazza\u0304r 7294<\/p>\n<p>Grade: <em>Hasan<\/em> (fair) according to Al-Albani<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\">\u0639\u064e\u0646 \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0633\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0646\u064e\u0651\u0628\u0650\u064a\u0651 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0647 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0645 <strong>\u0623\u064e\u064a\u064f\u0651 \u0627\u0644\u0652\u062e\u064e\u0644\u0652\u0642\u0650 \u0623\u064e\u0639\u0652\u062c\u064e\u0628\u064f \u0625\u0650\u064a\u0645\u064e\u0627\u0646\u064b\u0627 <\/strong>\u0642\u064e\u0